    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4411428>
    dc:description "FIGURES 30–41. Species of Vanima gen. nov., dorsal and ventral: 30–33. Vanima labe comb. nov.: 30–31. male (Chiriquí, Panama), 32–33. female (Verapaz, Mexico); 34–37. Vanima lesbia comb. nov.: 34–35. male (Amazonas, Brazil), 36–37. female (Amazonas, Brazil); 38–41. Vanima palladia comb. nov.: 38–39. Male (Acre, Brazil), 40–41. female (Acre, Brazil). Scale bar = 1 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4411428/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4411432>
    dc:description "FIGURES 45–46. Wing venation of Vanima palladia comb. nov.: 45. male, 46. female. Black arrows indicate generic diagnostic features. Scale bar = 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4411432/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4411456>
    dc:description "FIGURE 87. Phylogenetic tree showing the position of Vareuptychia stat. rest. (green) and Vanima gen. nov. (purple) in Euptychiina. Numbers above the branches indicate the support values (SH-aLRT support/ultrafast bootstrap support); numbers below 70 are not shown." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4411456/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

